data.description: $12,000 PRICE REDUCTION - MOTIVATED SELLERS - EXCLUSIVE LENDER INCENTIVE - NO METRO TAX - LOW HOA - MAKE AN OFFER!  Nestled on a peaceful cul-de-sac in desirable Monarch Estates, this impressive home offers an intelligent layout, luxurious finishes, and a prime location, this property truly has it all. The main level welcomes you with a versatile room, designed as a bedroom or office, perfect for accommodating various needs and pristine hardwood floors that flow seamlessly throughout the open living spaces. The expansive living area is bathed in natural light and extends effortlessly to the kitchen, complete with granite countertops, gas range plus double ovens, a large island and ample cabinetry. The upper level is a haven of relaxation and convenience, featuring three well-appointed bedrooms thoughtfully situated for optimal privacy. The large master bedroom is a retreat in itself, offering a cozy sitting area, an en-suite bathroom adorned with a luxury shower, and an expansive walk-in closet. A generously sized loft space on this level provides an ideal space for recreation, entertainment, or relaxation. The upper-level laundry room ensures practicality is effortlessly woven into the fabric of this home. The full, unfinished basement, offers endless potential for customization to suit your specific preferences and needs. Situated on an expansive corner lot, with two stamped concrete patios for outdoor entertaining. The open space across from the home not only enhances the visual appeal but also offers a unique opportunity for outdoor activities and leisure. Centennial Elementary School is within walking distance, and commuting is a breeze with easy access to I-25, facilitating efficient travel to various destinations.
